snippet.title: Texas Prison Stories
snippet.description:
Tim Sno is a single father and sole provider of a beautiful 3 year old baby girl named Ella Rose. Thank you for watching this channel and subscribing to the podcast! Everyone of you are helping to change our lives for the better. We love our Texas Prison Stories family!

The CashApp to donate to this channel or anybody mentioned on this channel (just put their name on it) is $TexasPrisonStories https://cash.app/$TexasPrisonStories

The Texas Prison Stories Podcast is https://www.anchor.fm/texas-prison-stories

Tim's Twitter is @PrisonTexas https://twitter.com/PrisonTexas

Tim's Instagram is https://www.instagram.com/texasprisonstoriesonyoutube

Tim's TikTok is https://www.tiktok.com/@timsno409

Tim's Teespring is https://teespring.com/stores/texasprisonstories

Tim's Facebook Group is https://www.facebook.com/groups/289293636097640
